examples.text: Bazen arzularıma direnirim özgürlüğümü hissetmek için.
examples.translation: Sometimes I resist my desires in order to feel I'm free.

examples.text: Siz beni istemeseniz yine kararımda direneceğim.
examples.translation: If you don't want me, I will still insist on my decision.

etymology: Inherited from Ottoman Turkish ذیرنمك, from Proto-Turkic *ti-. Passive form of diremek.
